MILDRED G. VESPER, v. FLORIDA INDUSTRIAL COMMISSION UNEMPLOYMENT DIVISION, and LEROY O. WATERS. 23 So. (2nd) 528

June Term, 1945

October 12, 1945 Division B Rehearing denied November 8, 1945 Robert C. Lane and Alfred E. Sapp, for appellant. Burnis T. Coleman, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The order appealed from is affirmed.

It is so ordered.

TERRELL, BUFORD, BROWN, ADAMS and SEBRING, JJ., concur. CHAPMAN, C. J., and THOMAS, J., dissent.
